/* Editor — Credentials → Container Registries */
"Container Registries" = "Container Registries";
"Per-registry HTTP Basic auth for `docker pull` / `docker push`. The real password is never written into the VM — bromure puts a fake `base64(\"<user>:<derived>\")` in `~/.docker/config.json`, and the proxy substitutes the real value on the wire when the request hits the matching registry host." = "Per-registry HTTP Basic auth for `docker pull` / `docker push`. The real password is never written into the VM — bromure puts a fake `base64(\"<user>:<derived>\")` in `~/.docker/config.json`, and the proxy substitutes the real value on the wire when the request hits the matching registry host.";
